{"tid":1761504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(政治審查) 台灣賣座大片《返校》被香港四大戲院商拒映?","createTime":"2019-11-29T03:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T01:29:05.000Z","uid":134071,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"701dbb1a9e0d3d95ea52f1bb5f2beafe818b4864","tid":1761504,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"講述台灣極權暴政時代既驚悚電影《返校》, 在台灣票房勁收, 成為台灣史上的本土驚悚電影票房亞軍 (僅次於《色戒》)<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%BF#%E5%85%A8%E5%8F%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2588%25BF%23%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%258F%25B0&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=fadc39cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%BF#%E5%85%A8%E5%8F%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n不過, 之前已經有報導指香港大部分戲院商都拒映《返校》(只有6間戲院願意安排上畫), 而且可能跟《返校》被中共封殺有關.<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/entertainment/player?newsId=370706&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D370706%26refer%3D&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=416c3971\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D370706%26refer%3D&h=6b9c6f01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/entertainment/player?newsId=370706&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n事實上, 《返校》雖然在12月5日香港上映, 但在<strong>香港四大戲院商的下期上映欄目, 完全沒有《返校》.</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cinema.com.hk/tc/movie/upcoming\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinema.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fmovie%2Fupcoming&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=f337ece0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cinema.com.hk/tc/movie/upcoming</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.goldenharvest.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldenharvest.com%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=45846442\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.goldenharvest.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uacinemas.com.hk/chi/movies#coming\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uacinemas.com.hk%2Fchi%2Fmovies%23coming&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=f792b4e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uacinemas.com.hk/chi/movies#coming</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mclcinema.com/ComingSoon.aspx?visLang=1&amp;gv=0&amp;y=2019&amp;mo=12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mclcinema.com%2FComingSoon.aspx%3FvisLang%3D1%26gv%3D0%26y%3D2019%26mo%3D12&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=583457d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mclcinema.com/ComingSoon.aspx?visLang=1&amp;gv=0&amp;y=2019&amp;mo=12</a><br />\n<br />\n《返校》本身極具商業性 (賣座驚悚電影+故事題材迎合當今香港時勢), 而且係12月5日上映既其他電影當中, 只有《豔舞大盜》較有商業性.  各大戲院不願上映《返校》,  明顯唔係單純商業判斷.  而係自我政治審查.<br />\n家,<br />\n咁就真係好奇怪.  《返校》係反極權暴政, 但就無直接鼓吹台獨與港獨; 而家, 單純反極權暴政, 係香港都係禁片?  <br />\n而且, 中共在2018年初封殺《1987：逆權公民》後, 香港四大戲院商依然照上《1987：逆權公民》.  <br />\n點解《1987：逆權公民》上年可以上,  《返校》今年反而唔上得?    香港自由係一年間退步到咁快?<br />\n<br />\n而且, 區議會選舉已經證明香港觀眾民意. 香港四大戲院商卻依然搶先在旗下戲院實行「一國一制」, 係咪跟香港市民對著幹?"},{"pid":"2c7b00721574ddde2a0925bf0ce5795d727f9ed6","tid":1761504,"uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:23:19.000Z","msg":"香港試片觀眾: 《返校》可激勵香港人心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191120/60288658\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191120%2F60288658&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=e41d0f31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191120%2F60288658&h=ea8316d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191120/60288658</a><br />\n<br />\n事實上近日香港逆權運動轉趨激烈，而《返》校情節跟香港目前情況不謀而合，如憲兵毒打學生、限制學生人身自由的劇情，都令港人感觸良多。有看過試片的觀眾更表示，<strong>在最後一幕時很有衝動大叫口號</strong>，可想而知此片如何激勵人心。"},{"pid":"cca311d9bcd89f1eb40e82a97718d5ce54fd7456","tid":1761504,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"仲有哩幾間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wmoov.com/movie/showtimes/46891?ref=moviePost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwmoov.com%2Fmovie%2Fshowtimes%2F46891%3Fref%3DmoviePost&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=5f271745\" target=\"_blank\">https://wmoov.com/movie/showtimes/46891?ref=moviePost</a>"},{"pid":"daa701c88de314d7edcc7967fe3d0b6102e1dd74","tid":1761504,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cca311d9bcd89f1eb40e82a97718d5ce54fd7456","tid":1761504,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"仲有哩幾間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wmoov.com/movie/showtimes/46891?ref=moviePost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwmoov.com%2Fmovie%2Fshowtimes%2F46891%3Fref%3DmoviePost&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=5f271745\" target=\"_blank\">https://wmoov.com/movie/showtimes/46891?ref=moviePost</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且, 星期六+星期日既優先場未滿哂, 要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"h